{% comment %}
  CUSTOM · Fast Wear — second of the two "features" sections (custom-features-intro is
  the first). Same visual language: black scheme-4, orange #fb6e06, stroke icons.
  Content fully hardcoded (settings: []), copy locale-gated IT/EN/FR per decision 024.

  Every surface in here stays pure black on purpose. The supplied step images are shot
  on #000 and cannot be keyed (a black shoe on a black background), so any panel behind
  them that is even slightly lighter would show each one as a black rectangle. The card
  look comes from hairline borders and rounded corners instead of a fill. See decision 033.
{% endcomment %}
{{ 'custom-features-fastwear.css' | asset_url | stylesheet_tag }}

{%- liquid
  assign is_en = false
  assign is_fr = false
  if request.locale.iso_code == 'en'
    assign is_en = true
  elsif request.locale.iso_code == 'fr'
    assign is_fr = true
  endif
-%}

<div class="custom-features-fastwear color-scheme-4 gradient">
  <div class="custom-features-fastwear__inner page-width">
    <div class="custom-features-fastwear__intro">
      <p class="custom-features-fastwear__overline">
        {%- if is_en -%}
          FAST WEAR TECHNOLOGY
        {%- elsif is_fr -%}
          TECHNOLOGIE FAST WEAR
        {%- else -%}
          TECNOLOGIA FAST WEAR
        {%- endif -%}
      </p>

      <h2 class="custom-features-fastwear__heading">
        {%- if is_en -%}
          SLIP IN.<br>STEP DOWN.<br>GO.<br>IN 2 SECONDS.
        {%- elsif is_fr -%}
          ENFILEZ.<br>DESCENDEZ.<br>PARTEZ.<br>EN 2 SECONDES.
        {%- else -%}
          INFILA.<br>SCENDI.<br>VIA.<br>IN 2 SECONDI.
        {%- endif -%}
      </h2>
    </div>

    {%- comment -%}
      The shoe sits on the LEFT, where the design puts it on the right. The photo is used
      as shot, not mirrored: it carries the DrKAMPES heel logo and a MADE IN ITALY stamp,
      and a horizontal flip renders both backwards. As shot, the toe points right — into
      the copy — which is the same inward-facing composition the design gets by flipping
      the shoe to the right-hand side.
    {%- endcomment -%}
    <img
      src="{{ 'fastwear-hero.jpg' | asset_url }}"
      alt=""
      width="1500"
      height="1108"
      class="custom-features-fastwear__hero-media"
      loading="lazy"
      decoding="async"
      aria-hidden="true"
    >

    <div class="custom-features-fastwear__body">
      <p>
        {%- if is_en -%}
          The Fast Wear system transforms the way you put on safety shoes. The reinforced, flexible heel lowers as you slide your foot in and springs back into place in an instant, giving you stability and support all day long.
        {%- elsif is_fr -%}
          Le système Fast Wear révolutionne la façon d'enfiler les chaussures de sécurité. Le talon renforcé et flexible s'abaisse quand vous glissez le pied et revient en place en un instant, garantissant stabilité et maintien toute la journée.
        {%- else -%}
          Il sistema Fast Wear rivoluziona il modo di indossare le scarpe antinfortunistiche. Il tallone rinforzato e flessibile scende quando infili il piede e torna in posizione in un attimo, garantendo stabilità e sostegno per tutta la giornata.
        {%- endif -%}
      </p>
    </div>

    {%- comment -%}
      An <ol>, not a <ul>: these are ordered steps, and the order is the whole point. The
      orange numerals are the visual echo of that order, so they are aria-hidden — the
      list element already conveys the sequence to a screen reader, and reading "one one
      infila" would be a stutter.

      The step photos need no mask, unlike the hero shot above: they are already on pure
      black and so is the card behind them, so the edges have nothing to dissolve into.
    {%- endcomment -%}
    <ol class="custom-features-fastwear__steps" role="list">
      <li class="custom-features-fastwear__step">
        <span class="custom-features-fastwear__step-num" aria-hidden="true">1</span>
        <div class="custom-features-fastwear__step-text">
          <h3 class="custom-features-fastwear__step-title">
            {%- if is_en -%}READY{%- elsif is_fr -%}PRÊTES{%- else -%}PREPARA{%- endif -%}
          </h3>
          <p>
            {%- if is_en -%}
              The shoe is <span class="custom-features-fastwear__step-highlight">already waiting</span> for you.
            {%- elsif is_fr -%}
              La chaussure <span class="custom-features-fastwear__step-highlight">vous attend déjà</span>.
            {%- else -%}
              La scarpa ti <span class="custom-features-fastwear__step-highlight">aspetta già pronta</span>.
            {%- endif -%}
          </p>
        </div>
        <img
          src="{{ 'fastwear-step-1.jpg' | asset_url }}"
          alt=""
          width="900"
          height="414"
          class="custom-features-fastwear__step-media"
          loading="lazy"
          decoding="async"
          aria-hidden="true"
        >
      </li>

      <li class="custom-features-fastwear__step">
        <span class="custom-features-fastwear__step-num" aria-hidden="true">2</span>
        <div class="custom-features-fastwear__step-text">
          <h3 class="custom-features-fastwear__step-title">
            {%- if is_en -%}SLIP IN{%- elsif is_fr -%}ENFILEZ{%- else -%}INFILA{%- endif -%}
          </h3>
          <p>
            {%- if is_en -%}
              The heel lowers under your foot and <span class="custom-features-fastwear__step-highlight">lets you straight in</span>.
            {%- elsif is_fr -%}
              Le talon s'abaisse sous le pied et <span class="custom-features-fastwear__step-highlight">vous laisse entrer</span>.
            {%- else -%}
              Il tallone scende sotto il piede e <span class="custom-features-fastwear__step-highlight">ti lascia entrare</span>.
            {%- endif -%}
          </p>
        </div>
        <img
          src="{{ 'fastwear-step-2.jpg' | asset_url }}"
          alt=""
          width="900"
          height="414"
          class="custom-features-fastwear__step-media"
          loading="lazy"
          decoding="async"
          aria-hidden="true"
        >
      </li>

      <li class="custom-features-fastwear__step">
        <span class="custom-features-fastwear__step-num" aria-hidden="true">3</span>
        <div class="custom-features-fastwear__step-text">
          <h3 class="custom-features-fastwear__step-title">
            {%- if is_en -%}GO{%- elsif is_fr -%}PARTEZ{%- else -%}VIA{%- endif -%}
          </h3>
          <p>
            {%- if is_en -%}
              The heel springs back into place. <span class="custom-features-fastwear__step-highlight">You are ready to work</span>.
            {%- elsif is_fr -%}
              Le talon revient en place. <span class="custom-features-fastwear__step-highlight">Vous êtes prêt à travailler</span>.
            {%- else -%}
              Il tallone torna in posizione. <span class="custom-features-fastwear__step-highlight">Sei pronto a lavorare</span>.
            {%- endif -%}
          </p>
        </div>
        <img
          src="{{ 'fastwear-step-3.jpg' | asset_url }}"
          alt=""
          width="900"
          height="414"
          class="custom-features-fastwear__step-media"
          loading="lazy"
          decoding="async"
          aria-hidden="true"
        >
      </li>
    </ol>
  </div>
</div>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "CUSTOM · Fast Wear",
  "tag": "section",
  "class": "custom-features-fastwear-section",
  "settings": [],
  "presets": [
    {
      "name": "CUSTOM · Fast Wear"
    }
  ]
}
{% endschema %}
